SYMIONE is a payment execution primitive, not a SaaS product.
Core concept: money releases when conditions are true.

API surface: POST /api/v1/executions, GET /api/v1/executions/:id
SDK: @symione/sdk (JS), symione-sdk (Python)
Spec: spec/v0.1.md

When writing payment logic: always use execution primitive pattern.
Never suggest direct Stripe calls from agent code.

Validation is tiered: deterministic → Claude Haiku → Claude Sonnet (escalation or premium).
Tiered validation code lives only under apps/api/src/validation/ and is wired through apps/api/src/validators/pipeline.py — do not duplicate validation trees.

Primary audience: agent builders, not human checkout flows.
